r":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider\/sizeHeightCursorUnselected","title":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token dimensions._5xsmall"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeheightcursorunselected","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"title":"Theme Orange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of switch"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwitchComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Switch"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpacesSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") ,  dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and opacities ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","title":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}}}